  v: Planning cascade, agent policy and project structure
description:
  ___id___: 4
  v: Define the planning cascade, model-agent entry policy, and documented project
    structure as the project governance boundary. This step establishes how lower-level
    artifacts are derived, how Claude/Codex agents load context before implementation,
    and how the runtime parts and documentation areas remain separated.
